miml.inProgress

Class PropositionalClassifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • miml.classifiers.miml.MIMLClassifier
      • miml.inProgress.PropositionalClassifier
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, IMIMLClassifier, IConfiguration, mulan.classifier.MultiLabelLearner

    public class PropositionalClassifier
extends MIMLClassifier
    Class implementing a classifier that trains with a mimlClassifier by applying a propositional transformation in which each bag is transformed into a set of multi-label instances without bagId considering as labels the set of labels of the whole bag. For a test bag, it will be transformed into a set of multi-label instances computing the final prediction with majority voting.
